  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\nFor low gas price `truffle migrate` ended with a timeout error. I set low gas price (6 Gwei) because my contracts need about 8*10^6 of gas. I can wait for a couple of hours for contracts deploying, it's OK for me. I find this line in the truffle-contract module:\r\n\r\n`var timeout = C.synchronization_timeout || 240000;`\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nset low gas price in truffle network configuration\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nall contracts are deployed\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\nThe error occurred during `truffle migrate`: \"Error: Transaction 0x... wasn't processed in 240 seconds!\"\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: ubuntu 16.04\r\n* Truffle version: 4.0.1\r\n* Ethereum client: infura mainnet\r\n* node version: 8.2.1\r\n* npm version: 5.3.0\r\n",
